00:23:36.776 --> 00:23:39.876
just represents preliminary data to set up the framework of the model.

403
00:23:41.296 --> 00:23:44.356
And now I'll get into some of the analyses I've done on each of the modalities

404
00:23:44.376 --> 00:23:48.356
independently. So for our 19 sample cohort, we had a neuropathologist at

