00:26:24.424 --> 00:26:27.914
relevant and niche information that you wouldn't be able to pick up with your eye

451
00:26:27.964 --> 00:26:31.854
alone. We'll then add an output head specifically for the task of

452
00:26:31.884 --> 00:26:35.524
recurrence prediction. And we can visualize the results of this fine-tuning through

