01:17:34.438 --> 01:17:37.468
microenvironment is so harsh for these cell therapies.

1335
01:17:37.538 --> 01:17:40.808
And so based on the spatial transcriptomics approaches that we've

1336
01:17:41.058 --> 01:17:44.658
